CP 541 of 1989 IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICTURE AT BOMBAY ORDINARY ORIGINAL CIVIL JURISDICTION COMPANY PETITION NO.541 OF 1989 WITH OFFICIAL LIQUIDATOR'S REPORT DATED 18 07 2012 M/s.Premier Automobiles Limited .....Petitioner Versus M/s.Dhoot Agencies Private Limited (in Liqn.) ..Respondent Mrs.Manasi Jadhav, for ICICI Bank Ltd. Dr.T.Pandian, Official Liquidator, present.

CORAM: S.J.KATHAWALLA, J.

DATE: 9 th AUGUST 2012

P.C. : . Perused the valuation report submitted by Shri Mahendra Bodhe. He has valued the movable properties at Rs.76,000/ . In view thereof, the reserved bid is fixed at Rs.80,000/ . EMD shall be 25% of the reserve bid. Since the properties are worth approximately Rs.80,000/ only, the Official Liquidator shall advertise the sale of the movable properties by private treaty i.e. by displaying the sale notice on the web sites of this Hon'ble Court, Official Liquidator, High Court Bombay and the Ministry of Corporate Affairs, on the notice board of the Official Liquidator, DRT, Mumbai and also by sending the sale notice to the buyers who usually take part in the auction conducted by the Official Liquidator. ssp /2 CP 541 of 1989 . Prayer (d) of the Report is allowed. . The Official Liquidator's Report is accordingly disposed of. ( S.J.KATHAWALLA, J. ) ssp /2
